Rename to pim-config.json. Should contain a JSON object of this form:

{
    "subscriptions": {
        "NAME1": {
            "id": "SUBSCRIPTION-GUID",
            "aks_resource_group": "my-resource-group",
            "aks_cluster_name": "my-cluster"
        },
        "NAME2": {
            "id": "SUBSCRIPTION-GUID-2",
            "aks_resource_group": "",
            "aks_cluster_name": ""
        }
    },
    "default_duration": "PT8H",
    "default_justification": "Development on Project"
}

Subscription entries can also be plain strings (just the ID) for activate-only use.
AKS fields are required for --switch mode.
